{"tid":348601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「路西法」熱浪捲歐，意大利南部55℃！！","createTime":"2017-08-05T23:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T01:44:29.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"549163c62d78bec0a1a65bc13ff8717bba492c7e","tid":348601,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T23:40:34.000Z","msg":"歐洲南部和東部受到被形容為「魔鬼」（Lucifer）的熱浪侵襲，普遍高達逾40℃的歷史高度，歐洲氣象網站Meteoalarm向10國發出最高級別的紅色警告，至少兩人因酷熱天氣死亡。<br />\n熱浪情況以意大利和巴爾幹半島最為嚴重。意大利氣溫比歷年同期平均高出10℃，羅馬錄得43℃高溫，南部那不勒斯一帶更達55℃，中部佛羅倫斯一間藝術博物館因冷氣失靈閉館。"},{"pid":"47bc993a92cffb47214c134f7847fdc5131e4663","tid":348601,"uid":48902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T23:50:44.000Z","msg":"歐洲夏天同冬天不嬲死得多人"},{"pid":"c1e1d18ce73afd45570e82d5b9f241cd4e1056a0","tid":348601,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T23:52:00.000Z","msg":"問左香港濕熱未"},{"pid":"2b55e7ffae6104dc71b5de21e7b64cee1a476719","tid":348601,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T23:52:01.000Z","msg":"香港濕熱勁d?"},{"pid":"16e1dc8343507ea711fbd1dcb904aee980f796fa","tid":348601,"uid":629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T00:09:25.000Z","msg":"上年6月去都係30度左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11fb22d2951154a8ce70d0b64d4579ae189c708","tid":348601,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T00:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 地獄咁"},{"pid":"31929940f766b9fdfefbf50e01e428fccd0a8e3b","tid":348601,"uid":132038,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T00:19:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"105e2d2320783aa0594adaa48afb0dea16cfe412","tid":348601,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T00:44:16.000Z","msg":"唔好開冷氣，慳電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be95bd61c152e76f7cbf8a